# ELEVON ERP — Design System

## Brand identity

- **Brand name:** ELEVON ERP
- **Logo files:** `src/assets/images/brand/` — `coreerp-mark-light.svg`, `coreerp-mark-dark.svg`, `coreerp-logo-light.svg`, `coreerp-logo-dark.svg` (filenames kept as-is; contents are ELEVON hexagonal navy+gold E-mark)
- **Theme:** Deep navy (#070e1b) background + brass/gold (#cca55b → #f0d87a) accents
- **Default mode:** **dark** (localStorage key `erp_theme_mode`, fallback `'dark'`)

## Color palette (CSS variables — `erp-estate-tokens.scss`)

### Navy scale
```css
--navy-900: #0e1f33   /* primary dark, active buttons */
--navy-800: #14283f
--navy-700: #1b3553
--navy-600: #22436a
--navy-500: #2b5280
```

### Brass / Gold scale
```css
--brass-600: #8a6420
--brass-500: #b48a40   /* main accent */
--brass-400: #cca55b
--brass-300: #e8c97a   /* hover borders */
--brass-100: #f4e7c4   /* active text on dark buttons */
```

### Semantic paper / ink
```css
--paper:    #f6f2ea    /* light mode page bg */
--paper-2:  #ede8de    /* light mode muted bg */
--surface:  #fffdf8    /* light mode card bg */

--ink-900:  #0e1f33    /* primary text */
--ink-700:  #2d3f53
--ink-500:  #6b7f96    /* muted text */
--ink-400:  #8fa0b3    /* subtle text */
--ink-300:  #b4c2d0
```

### Dark mode overrides (applied via `[data-theme='dark']`)
```css
--paper:    #070e1b
--paper-2:  #0a1525
--surface:  #111e30
--surface-2:#162540
--sidebar-bg: linear-gradient(180deg, #05101e 0%, #070e1b 50%, #060c18 100%)
--header-bg:  rgba(7, 14, 27, 0.96)
```

### Status colors
```css
--ok:      #16a34a   --ok-bg:   rgba(22,163,74,0.10)
--warn:    #d97706   --warn-bg: rgba(217,119,6,0.10)
--bad:     #dc2626   --bad-bg:  rgba(220,38,38,0.10)
