## Typography

```css
--font-display: 'Instrument Serif', 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif
--font-ui:      'Inter', 'IBM Plex Sans Arabic', 'Cairo', system-ui
--font-body:    var(--font-ui)
--font-ar:      'IBM Plex Sans Arabic', 'Cairo', var(--font-ui)
--font-mono:    'JetBrains Mono', 'Geist Mono', monospace
```

RTL/Arabic: use `--font-ar` for body, `font-family: var(--font-ar)` when `html[dir='rtl']`.

## Spacing & radius

```css
--r-xs: 6px   --r-sm: 10px   --r: 14px   --r-lg: 20px   --r-xl: 28px
--pad-card: 20px   --pad-row: 14px
--sidebar-w: 248px   --sidebar-w-collapsed: 76px   --topbar-height: 64px
--erp-content-max: 1400px
```

## Motion

```css
--t-fast: 160ms   --t-med: 320ms   --t-slow: 520ms
--e-out:    cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1)
--e-spring: cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1)
```

## Dark mode rules

- Theme attribute: `document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dark'|'light')`
- Body classes: `theme-dark` / `theme-light`, `dark-mode` / `light-mode`, `flat-able-dark`
- Always write dark overrides as `[data-theme='dark'] .your-class { }` in the same SCSS file
- Never use `prefers-color-scheme` media query — the service manages theme explicitly

## Page layout pattern

```html
<section class="erp-page erp-list-page erp-estate-fade-up">
  <app-page-header [titleKey]="'MODULE.TITLE'">
    <div header-actions>
      <button class="erp-button erp-button--primary">...</button>
    </div>
  </app-page-header>

  <div class="erp-card erp-list-page__card">
    <div class="erp-card__body">
      <app-data-table [columns]="cols" [data]="rows" [loading]="loading">
      </app-data-table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
```

## Key CSS classes (page-ui.scss + styles.scss)

### Cards
```css
.erp-card / .erp-list-page__card   /* 14px radius, card-bg, shadow-soft */
.erp-card__header                  /* 18/20px padding, border-bottom */
.erp-card__body                    /* padding: 0 (table fills it) */
```

### Buttons
```css
.erp-button--primary   /* navy gradient + gold border + cream text */
.erp-action-btn        /* 36×36px icon button, 10px radius */
.erp-action-btn--info / --success / --warning / --danger / --neutral
```

### Tables (rendered by `app-data-table`)
```css
.erp-table thead th   /* 10.5px, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.14em, text-align center */
.erp-table tbody td   /* 14px padding, text-align center, vertical-align middle */
```

### Pagination (inside `app-data-table`)
```css
.erp-table-pagination          /* flex space-between, border-top */
.erp-pagination-btn            /* 36×36px, 10px radius, transparent default */
.erp-pagination-btn.is-active  /* navy-900 bg + brass-100 text + navy shadow */
.erp-pagination-btn--nav       /* Prev/Next: border + surface bg */
```

### Search inside table toolbar
```css
.erp-table-search   /* directory-search style: flex row, icon+input, brass focus ring */
```

### Status badges
```html
<app-status-badge [status]="row.status" labelPrefix="STATUS."></app-status-badge>
```

### Skeleton loading
```html
<div class="skeleton-box" style="height:20px; width:80%; border-radius:4px;"></div>
```

## Sidebar & topbar SCSS files

| File | Scope |
|------|-------|
| `erp-estate-shell.scss` | Sidebar host, brand section, nav items, active indicator, topbar host |
| `erp-estate-tokens.scss` | All CSS variables (light + dark) |
| `erp-estate-utilities.scss` | Utility classes, animations (`erp-estate-fade-up`) |
| `page-ui.scss` | Shared cards, tables, pagination, buttons, page headers |
| `styles.scss` | Global Bootstrap overrides, dialog, form inputs, pagination component |

## i18n

- Translation files: `src/assets/i18n/ar.json` + `en.json`
- Pipe: `{{ 'KEY.PATH' | translate }}`
- Service: `TranslateService.instant('KEY')`
- Never hardcode Arabic or English strings in templates/components

## RTL / LTR

```html
<!-- HTML element gets dir from i18n service -->
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">   <!-- Arabic -->
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">   <!-- English -->
```

- Use `inset-inline-start/end` instead of `left/right` in SCSS for RTL-safe layouts
- Use `margin-inline` / `padding-inline` for horizontal spacing
- Test both directions when adding new layouts

## ApexCharts (dashboard)

- Import: `import ApexCharts from 'apexcharts'`
- Theme detection: read `document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-theme') === 'dark'`
- Chart colors palette: `['#3b82f6', '#10b981', '#f59e0b', '#8b5cf6', '#06b6d4', '#ec4899', '#f97316']`
- Prefer `area` type with gradient fill for time-series
- Tooltip theme: `'dark'` or `'light'` based on current theme

## DO NOT
- Use hardcoded hex colors in component SCSS — always use CSS variables
- Add `!important` unless overriding Bootstrap/third-party rules
- Use `left`/`right` CSS properties — use logical properties
- Add new global styles to `styles.scss` — use `page-ui.scss` or component SCSS
- Change the login screen layout (only color/shadow/glassmorphism improvements allowed)
